18
00:00:12,457 --> 00:00:15,457
http://hiqve.com/

19
00:00:18,481 --> 00:00:21,025
<i>Obi-Wan Kenobi in disguise!</i>

20
00:00:21,317 --> 00:00:24,195
<i>Working undercover
as assassin Rako Hardeen,</i>

21
00:00:24,278 --> 00:00:26,489
<i>Obi-Wan leads a secret mission to uncover</i>

22
00:00:26,572 --> 00:00:29,242
<i>the Separatist plot
against Chancellor Palpatine.</i>

23
00:00:29,951 --> 00:00:31,619
<i>Using cunning and courage,</i>

24
00:00:31,744 --> 00:00:34,413
<i>he gains the trust of
bounty hunter Cad Bane</i>

25
00:00:34,455 --> 00:00:36,916
<i>and criminal mastermind Moralo Eval,</i>

26
00:00:36,958 --> 00:00:40,962
<i>earning him entrance to the stronghold of
Separatist leader Count Dooku.</i>

27
00:00:41,587 --> 00:00:44,382
<i>Now it is here,
on the beautiful planet of Serenno,</i>

28
00:00:44,465 --> 00:00:48,302
<i>that a barbaric contest will determine
the fate of Obi-Wan Kenobi,</i>

29
00:00:48,469 --> 00:00:51,389
<i>and, possibly, the Republic itself.</i>

30
00:01:27,508 --> 00:01:31,262
Count Dooku, I apologize for my delay.

31
00:01:33,848 --> 00:01:38,227
Your careless delay
could have ruined my plan, Eval.

32
00:01:38,352 --> 00:01:41,772
I see Cad Bane is with you.
Who is the other one?

33
00:01:42,857 --> 00:01:45,359
This is Rako Hardeen.

34
00:01:45,443 --> 00:01:50,865
When Bane's escape plan failed,
we only succeeded thanks to Hardeen.

35
00:01:50,906 --> 00:01:53,951
I thought he might be
useful for the tournament.

36
00:01:54,243 --> 00:01:56,537
Enough small talk, I want my money.

37
00:01:56,579 --> 00:01:58,414
That makes two of us.

38
00:01:58,497 --> 00:02:02,501
You shall have it and perhaps much more.

39
00:02:02,543 --> 00:02:08,382
Both of you, if you would like to
enter our friendly little contest.

40
00:02:09,008 --> 00:02:11,052
I'm in, if he's in.

41
00:02:11,135 --> 00:02:15,890
You already owe me for one job, Dooku,
anything else will cost you triple.

42
00:02:16,265 --> 00:02:19,185
I assure you
that if you survive the challenge,

43
00:02:19,226 --> 00:02:21,395
the reward will be well worth it.

44
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:35,409
We have all the contestants we need.

45
00:02:36,369 --> 00:02:37,995
Prepare the tournament.

46
00:02:38,079 --> 00:02:39,872
Yes, My Lord.

47
00:02:56,639 --> 00:02:58,599
You summoned me, Master?

48
00:02:58,641 --> 00:03:03,312
Wrong to deceive you it was,
but much at stake there is.

49
00:03:03,688 --> 00:03:06,482
So I was right. Obi-Wan is still alive.

50
00:03:06,941 --> 00:03:10,778
Skywalker, a powerful Jedi you are,

51
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:14,573
yet unpredictable and dangerous
you can be.

52
00:03:15,074 --> 00:03:17,910
To both your friends and enemies.

53
00:03:18,619 --> 00:03:23,124
For Obi-Wan, on your patience
everything depends.

54
00:03:23,165 --> 00:03:24,917
What if he needs our help?

55
00:03:24,959 --> 00:03:26,127
Hmm.

56
00:03:26,168 --> 00:03:29,964
If you leave, help him you could.

57
00:03:30,089 --> 00:03:33,467
But his future, uncertain is.

58
00:03:34,301 --> 00:03:36,721
Trust in Obi-Wan we must.

59
00:03:48,107 --> 00:03:50,943
So what kind of
"friendly little contest"

60
00:03:50,985 --> 00:03:52,987
you think the Count's got planned?

61
00:03:53,070 --> 00:03:56,240
I'd be surprised if we all survive.

62
00:03:59,326 --> 00:04:01,412
Nice hat.

63
00:04:05,124 --> 00:04:06,500
Where did you get it?

64
00:04:19,555 --> 00:04:22,183
What are you looking at? It's a nice hat.

65
00:04:23,809 --> 00:04:25,686
Welcome to Serenno.

66
00:04:26,687 --> 00:04:28,105
You have been invited here

67
00:04:28,189 --> 00:04:31,525
because you are the best
bounty hunters in the galaxy.

68
00:04:32,485 --> 00:04:36,238
Kiera Swan, two-time winner of
the Obsidian Sphere.

69
00:04:36,405 --> 00:04:40,326
Derrown, known simply as
the exterminator.

70
00:04:40,659 --> 00:04:43,412
Sixtat, the Out lands Butcher.

71
00:04:43,496 --> 00:04:48,542
Embo, your bounty tallies
were second only to one last season.

72
00:04:48,584 --> 00:04:51,962
Cad Bane, who needs no introduction.

73
00:04:52,171 --> 00:04:55,925
Rako Hardeen,
the marksman of Concord Dawn.

74
00:04:56,217 --> 00:05:00,054
Jakoli, known for never
bringing anyone back alive.

75
00:05:00,805 --> 00:05:04,725
Onca, you and your brother
have been a legendary team.

76
00:05:04,850 --> 00:05:08,395
This challenge
may prove difficult for you alone.

77
00:05:08,562 --> 00:05:13,692
Twazzi, your acrobatics once earned you
praise from Chancellor Valorum.

78
00:05:13,734 --> 00:05:17,947
Sinrich, inventor of
the holographic disguise matrix.

79
00:05:18,030 --> 00:05:20,533
And, finally, Mantu.

80
00:05:20,574 --> 00:05:23,077
Your people were once a peaceful race.

81
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,412
How far they have fallen.

82
00:05:25,996 --> 00:05:30,167
In a few moments, all 11 of you will enter
what we call The Box.

83
00:05:43,931 --> 00:05:46,308
Some of you will not make it out alive.

84
00:05:46,392 --> 00:05:47,685
For those who do,

85
00:05:47,768 --> 00:05:51,021
we are looking for
the five most skilled among you.

86
00:05:51,105 --> 00:05:54,108
Any additional survivors will be eliminated

87
00:05:54,191 --> 00:05:58,237
to preserve the integrity of
the job that awaits you.

88
00:05:58,279 --> 00:06:00,531
Place your weapons here.

89
00:06:00,614 --> 00:06:05,286
For those we choose, you will, of course,
be paid most handsomely.

90
00:06:05,327 --> 00:06:08,914
But more than that, you will be a part of
an operation remembered as

91
00:06:08,956 --> 00:06:11,625
a turning point in the Clone Wars.

92
00:06:12,084 --> 00:06:13,878
And when we succeed,

93
00:06:13,961 --> 00:06:17,715
we will bring the Republic to
its pitiful knees.

94
00:06:17,798 --> 00:06:22,720
Listen up!
The Box was designed by me, Moralo Eval,

95
00:06:22,803 --> 00:06:27,641
to simulate certain situations
that might happen on the job.

96
00:06:28,017 --> 00:06:30,603
Go now, enter The Box,

97
00:06:30,978 --> 00:06:33,314
if you have the courage.

98
00:06:39,028 --> 00:06:43,532
That's it, everyone inside. Keep moving.

99
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:14,188
<i>Before we begin our first challenge,</i>

100
00:07:14,229 --> 00:07:18,651
<i>let me say there is only
one rule inside The Box.</i>

101
00:07:18,692 --> 00:07:20,527
<i>There are no rules.</i>

102
00:07:23,405 --> 00:07:27,701
<i>The point, my friend,
is to escape and quickly,</i>

103
00:07:27,743 --> 00:07:32,164
<i>because only the survivors
will advance to the next challenge.</i>

104
00:07:40,047 --> 00:07:42,758
Dioxis! Breathe it and you are dead!

105
00:07:47,179 --> 00:07:48,847
Every man for himself!

106
00:07:59,608 --> 00:08:01,402
That wasn't so hard.

107
00:08:18,919 --> 00:08:21,714
The way out isn't up. It's down.

108
00:08:21,755 --> 00:08:24,425
The filters in my helmet
can protect me for a short time.

109
00:08:24,466 --> 00:08:26,260
I'll scout a way out.

110
00:08:49,616 --> 00:08:52,411
There's a hole in the floor which
gets you below the gas line.

111
00:08:52,453 --> 00:08:54,496
Jump down the hole and follow the tunnel.

112
00:08:56,623 --> 00:08:58,208
What if he's wrong?

113
00:08:58,292 --> 00:09:00,419
You got a better idea?

114
00:09:26,445 --> 00:09:28,530
What took you so long?

115
00:09:36,163 --> 00:09:41,919
<i>Moralo Eval is impressed.
No casualties on the first challenge.</i>

116
00:09:42,878 --> 00:09:47,174
<i>I guarantee you
that will not be the case in the next.</i>

117
00:10:24,211 --> 00:10:29,174
Impressive. I sense
something different about that one.

118
00:10:29,967 --> 00:10:33,178
Tell me what you know
about this Rako Hardeen.

119
00:10:34,388 --> 00:10:37,724
He killed the Jedi Obi-Wan Kenobi.

120
00:10:37,766 --> 00:10:40,727
But only with a sniper rifle.

121
00:10:40,769 --> 00:10:43,605
Obi-Wan Kenobi?

122
00:11:00,247 --> 00:11:02,374
- I know how to get out!
- Show me.

123
00:11:02,416 --> 00:11:06,420
There's a pattern to the blades.
Watch, that one's next.

124
00:11:08,505 --> 00:11:11,175
If I can time it right,
I can climb up to that exit shaft.

125
00:11:12,885 --> 00:11:15,262
-Just follow me and time your jump.
-Go!

126
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:21,310
Get moving!

127
00:12:15,322 --> 00:12:17,532
Hardeen has done it again.

128
00:12:17,824 --> 00:12:21,995
I'm beginning to think he may be
the best one to lead this operation.

129
00:12:22,579 --> 00:12:26,333
Hardeen is crafty, I will grant you,

130
00:12:26,416 --> 00:12:31,129
but let's see what happens when
he is not the key to their survival.

131
00:12:39,179 --> 00:12:41,723
<i>To reach your final challenge,</i>

132
00:12:41,807 --> 00:12:44,351
<i>you must pass through my ray shield.</i>

133
00:12:54,569 --> 00:12:58,365
<i>The switch to turn it off
is on the other side.</i>

134
00:12:58,448 --> 00:13:03,912
<i>The syringe on the platform contains
a highly electrolytic serum</i>

135
00:13:03,996 --> 00:13:07,541
<i>that will allow you to
pass through the shield.</i>

136
00:13:08,375 --> 00:13:12,879
<i>However, it is toxic to all but one of you.</i>

137
00:13:19,303 --> 00:13:21,179
So it would seem.

138
00:13:43,243 --> 00:13:44,411
Ahhh!

139
00:13:53,587 --> 00:13:55,964
Hey, who put you in charge?

140
00:13:58,675 --> 00:14:01,303
Does anyone know
what this gas bag is saying?

141
00:14:01,386 --> 00:14:03,096
I do. He can get us out of this.

142
00:14:07,142 --> 00:14:10,520
He's a Parwan.
His blood can take the electrolytic serum.

143
00:14:12,147 --> 00:14:13,565
Are you certain?

144
00:14:13,607 --> 00:14:16,651
Fifty-fifty.
Depends on the blood type of the Parwan.

145
00:14:16,735 --> 00:14:18,028
Great.

146
00:14:28,622 --> 00:14:30,082
Hurry, use the serum.

147
00:15:22,926 --> 00:15:26,054
His blood. How did you know about it?

148
00:15:26,138 --> 00:15:28,265
I used to kill Parwans for a living.

149
00:15:34,521 --> 00:15:39,359
Your box does not appear to be
as much of a challenge as I thought.

150
00:15:39,401 --> 00:15:42,195
Perhaps I should put Hardeen
in charge of the mission.

151
00:15:43,071 --> 00:15:47,868
But this was my plan !
You promised me the lead role!

152
00:15:49,244 --> 00:15:53,498
You have one last test to change my mind.

153
00:15:54,207 --> 00:15:59,421
Do not fear, Count Dooku.
I will show you who is weak.

154
00:16:17,439 --> 00:16:20,233
<i>The final challenge has arrived.</i>

155
00:16:40,837 --> 00:16:43,590
Unfortunately, no.

156
00:16:55,477 --> 00:17:00,774
We are going to test your sniper skills.
Hit the target.

157
00:17:06,404 --> 00:17:10,492
Step back, boys,
I'll show you how it's done.

158
00:17:30,887 --> 00:17:34,599
I get it. If we miss the target,
this platform gets smaller.

159
00:17:34,641 --> 00:17:36,518
Soon there won't be any platform left.

160
00:17:55,453 --> 00:18:00,500
This is not the first time
you've saved everybody's skin, Hardeen.

161
00:18:00,542 --> 00:18:04,713
Five more hits.
Let's see how good you really are.

162
00:18:27,152 --> 00:18:28,737
Oh, what a shame,

163
00:18:29,112 --> 00:18:31,031
out of charges.

164
00:18:31,072 --> 00:18:34,826
It's also important as a bounty hunter
to be lucky,

165
00:18:34,868 --> 00:18:38,204
and your luck just ran out.

166
00:18:49,132 --> 00:18:52,510
How dare you defy Moralo Eval!

167
00:18:52,761 --> 00:18:55,680
If you're gonna kill him, do it like a man.

168
00:18:55,930 --> 00:18:57,891
<i>You heard him, Eval.</i>

169
00:19:01,811 --> 00:19:05,190
<i>Show us what you are really made of.</i>

170
00:19:40,141 --> 00:19:42,185
You're going to have to
do better than that!

171
00:19:42,602 --> 00:19:46,064
You, my friend,
have seen nothing yet!

172
00:20:03,623 --> 00:20:05,875
Let's even the playing field.

173
00:20:32,610 --> 00:20:34,237
<i>Finish him, Hardeen.</i>

174
00:20:38,575 --> 00:20:40,326
<i>Very disappointing.</i>

175
00:20:40,827 --> 00:20:45,165
All due respect, I just wanna do my job
and get my money.

176
00:20:46,791 --> 00:20:50,754
<i>lt is unfortunate
that your leadership skills are so lacking.</i>

177
00:20:50,837 --> 00:20:54,883
<i>And the rest,
congratulations on surviving The Box.</i>

178
00:20:55,383 --> 00:20:57,844
<i>Tomorrow you will
kidnap Chancellor Palpatine</i>

179
00:20:57,927 --> 00:20:59,929
<i>at the festival on Naboo.</i>

180
00:21:00,013 --> 00:21:02,932
<i>With the leader of The Republic
as our hostage,</i>

181
00:21:03,057 --> 00:21:07,061
<i>we will demand the release of
all Separatist prisoners.</i>

182
00:21:07,145 --> 00:21:11,608
<i>If our demand is not met,
the Chancellor will be executed.</i>

183
00:21:11,691 --> 00:21:14,944
<i>Either way,
you will help reshape the galaxy.</i>

184
00:21:15,361 --> 00:21:17,614
<i>Once you are all aboard the transport,</i>

185
00:21:17,697 --> 00:21:20,158
<i>Eval will walk you through his plan.</i>

186
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:24,370
<i>However, the operation on Naboo
will be run by</i>

187
00:21:24,412 --> 00:21:25,914
<i>Cad Bane.</i>

188
00:21:28,082 --> 00:21:31,252
<i>All of you work for him now.</i>

189
00:21:31,276 --> 00:21:36,276
http://hiqve.com/

